  "texts": [
    "(1988) argued that robustness should be an important determinant of trust.",
    "The robustness of AI refers to the reliability and consistency of its operations and results, including its performance under diverse and unexpected conditions (High-Level Expert Group on Artificial Intelligence (AI HLEG), 2019).",
    "The fairness of AI involves treating all users equitably, making unbiased decisions, and not",
    "10.3389/fpsyg.2024.1382693 Frontiers in Psychology 08 frontiersin.org",
    "discriminating against any group (Shin and Park, 2019)."
  ]
